地球的'''內核'''，是地球的最深層的部份，半徑1220公里<ref>{{Cite journal | first1=Marc | last1=Monnereau | first2=Marie | last2=Calvet | first3=Ludovic | last3=Margerin | first4=Annie | last4=Souriau | title=Lopsided Growth of Earth's Inner Core | journal=[[Science_(journal)|Science]] | date=May 21, 2010 | volume=328 | issue=5981 | pages=1014–1017 | doi=10.1126/science.1186212 | bibcode=2010Sci...328.1014M | pmid=20395477 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = E. R. Engdahl | author2 = E. A. Flynn | author3 = R. P. Massé | lastauthoramp=yes | title = Differential PkiKP travel times and the radius of the core | journal = Geophys. J. R. Astr. Soc.| volume = 40 | issue = 3 | pages = 457–463 | date = 1974 | doi = 10.1111/j.1365-246X.1974.tb05467.x|bibcode = 1974GeoJI..39..457E }}</ref>。一般相信它以[[鐵|鐵]]-[[鎳|鎳]]之[[合金|合金]]組成，以及大概與[[太陽|太陽]]表面溫度相同，約為5700[[開氏度|開氏度]]。
==温度与压力==
内地核的温度与压力可以通过理论与试验方式估计出铁在内地核与外地核边界压力（约330 GPa）时的融化温度。温度估计为{{convert|5700|K|sigfig=2}}。<ref name="alfè">{{cite journal | author = D. Alfè | author2 = M. Gillan | author3 = G. D. Price | lastauthoramp = yes | title = Composition and temperature of the Earth's core constrained by combining ab initio calculations and seismic data | journal = Earth and Planetary Science Letters | volume = 195 | issue = 1–2 | pages = 91–98 | publisher = [[Elsevier|Elsevier]] | date = January 30, 2002 | url = http://www.homepages.ucl.ac.uk/~ucfbdxa/pubblicazioni/epsl2002.pdf | format = PDF | doi = 10.1016/S0012-821X(01)00568-4 | bibcode = 2002E&PSL.195...91A | access-date = 2018-12-15 | archive-date = 2019-02-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190203125634/http://www.homepages.ucl.ac.uk/~ucfbdxa/pubblicazioni/epsl2002.pdf | dead-url = yes }}</ref> 内地核的压强略高于内外地核边界：估计在{{convert|330|to|360|GPa|atm}}。<ref name="crc">{{cite book | editor = David. R. Lide | title = CRC Handbook of Chemistry and Physics | pages = j14–13 | edition = 87th | date = 2006–2007 | url = http://hbcpnetbase.com/ | access-date = 2018-12-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170724011402/http://www.hbcpnetbase.com/ | archive-date = 2017-07-24 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>铁在这么高的压力下是固体，因为其[[熔点|熔点]]随压力戏剧性增高（参见[[克劳修斯－克拉佩龙方程|克劳修斯－克拉佩龙方程]]）。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Anneli Aitta | title = Iron melting curve with a tricritical point | journal = Journal of Statistical Mechanics: Theory and Experiment | volume = 2006 | issue = 12 | date = 2006-12-01 | pages = 12015–12030 | publisher = iop | url = http://stacks.iop.org/JSTAT/2006/P12015 | doi = 10.1088/1742-5468/2006/12/P12015 | arxiv = cond-mat/0701283 | bibcode = 2006JSMTE..12..015A | access-date = 2018-12-15 | archive-date = 2019-09-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190913011202/https://iopscience.iop.org/article/10.1088/1742-5468/2006/12/P12015 | dead-url = no }} or see preprints https://arxiv.org/pdf/cond-mat/0701283 , https://arxiv.org/pdf/0807.0187 .</ref>

''Science''杂志上的一篇论文 <ref>{{cite journal | author = S. Anzellini | author2 = A. Dewaele | author3 = M. Mezouar | author4 = P. Loubeyre | author5 = G. Morard | lastauthoramp = yes | title = Melting of Iron at Earth’s Inner Core Boundary Based on Fast X-ray Diffraction | journal = Science | volume = 340 | issue = 6136 | date = 2013 | pages = 464–466 | publisher = AAAS | url = http://www.sciencemag.org/content/340/6131/464 | doi = 10.1126/science.1233514 | bibcode = 2013Sci...340..464A | access-date = 2018-12-15 | archive-date = 2015-11-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151104184657/http://www.sciencemag.org/content/340/6131/464 | dead-url = no }}</ref>认为内地核边界铁的熔点是6230 ± 500 K。

